\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 That night, nigel was in pain. HIs inner thighs brused from the hours of riding\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92 but eh was genial and solicitous, and from time to time he woudl get up from his cmp chair to speak tenderly to soran, to stroke his muzzle and feed him flatbreads. }
