\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b1\i0 You might trvel to escape the self, but in the desert of all places, where there is little else, you are thrown back upon your mind and your body with intensified force. Quietness offers no liberation, after all: there had been midnights when I swear my libido - whatever it consists of - was audible (somewhere between a stiff door and a backed up drain). Nope, the body was there; the body was there more than ever, and with it all its claims.}
