\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Tinnitus, deafness, reaction from noiselessness of the deasert}
\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Without witnesses, how do you conduct yourself? In the secrecy of any imagination, to what extremes might the mind wander? I\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92d found I was drawn to the lawlessness of the desert; not only the way norms might be suspended but how, in the absence of regulation or judgement, the word good itself was loosed from meaning. }
