\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 In china, people exiled to the desert. Families of criminals who had been executed for, say, murder, or incest, or treason. Disgraced government officials, or troublemakers, who had criticised official corruption or associated with ocnvicted trators. Ttooed on both temples like a double stamp of lading: your crime on the right; on the left your destination. }
