\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Whereas for indigenous australians the desert is an infinite mosaic of symbols and storie, they hyper-arid deserts of china have figured as mere interstices, or collectively as a dread realm entered under duress or to reach the next oasis, even among those who populate the desert\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s edge. }
