\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 It was impossible to know where one named desert ended and the next began, where Gobi became black gobi, where gashun gobi degenerated into the kumtag desert and the salt-fields of lop nor, where the threshold was between lop nor, and the taklamakan. And no sooner had I established that one desert lay here and another there, or that this one abutted that, than I read or was told that, no, the black gobi ends here and teh gashun gobi is not there, but five hundred kilometers north.}
