\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Personal friendships were slightly scorned in the toostrong mental atmosphere of evangilne\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s home, where anything approaching sentimentality was anathema. She herself was \u8216\'91robustuous, obstreperous, and rebellious, and convinced that there was something so essentially wrong with the world that nothing but revolution could set it right. }
